      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "应用场景",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "BXBpxvYOi4iJgC0GewdE2",
      "originalText": "应用场景",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KQrHzi6AVO7mnmP-SmM1l",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -626.4905827056812,
      "y": 3295.052617777971,
      "width": 471.19976806640625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RnfKwmtXkJeJpREnemny7",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1425220895,
      "version": 543,
      "versionNonce": 1275405976,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CopyOnWriteArrayList 的应用场景主要有两个方面：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CopyOnWriteArrayList 的应用场景主要有两个方面：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "dITKn5IWJ9udAakUAJJm-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -625.5614987545846,
      "y": 3328.6348307992844,
      "width": 156.6599884033203,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RnfKwmtXkJeJpREnemny7",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 51675217,
      "version": 574,
      "versionNonce": 1060646632,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.读多写少的场景",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.读多写少的场景",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "r9SVl6xo5z5584nG-pV7X",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -618.3468722439925,
      "y": 3367.6563567453472,
      "width": 565.0778959815998,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RnfKwmtXkJeJpREnemny7",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1185884479,
      "version": 648,
      "versionNonce": 315921304,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "由于 CopyOnWriteArrayList 的读操作不需要加锁，因此它非常\n适合在读多写少的场景中使用。例如，一个读取频率比写入频率\n高得多的缓存，使用 CopyOnWriteArrayList 可以提高读取性\n能，并减少锁竞争的开销。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "由于 CopyOnWriteArrayList 的读操作不需要加锁，因此它非常适合在读多写少的场景中使用。例如，一个读取频率比写入频率高得多的缓存，使用 CopyOnWriteArrayList 可以提高读取性能，并减少锁竞争的开销。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PwgfBnhdKp2Z32lo9PGyL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -627.419666656778,
      "y": 3513.487194490142,
      "width": 216.6599884033203,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RnfKwmtXkJeJpREnemny7",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 505564721,
      "version": 619,
      "versionNonce": 555880936,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.不需要实时更新的数据",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.不需要实时更新的数据",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NKx_KIbqRq41Ki47A-gHz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -622.6250046236162,
      "y": 3554.3668883383984,
      "width": 557.5090887637516,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "RnfKwmtXkJeJpREnemny7",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 110471519,
      "version": 831,
      "versionNonce": 120479896,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "由于 CopyOnWriteArrayList 读取的数据可能不是最新的，因此\n它适合于不需要实时更新的数据。例如，在日志应用中，为了\n保证应用的性能，日志记录的操作可能被缓冲，并不是实时写\n入文件系统，而是在某个时刻批量写入。这种情况下，使用\nCopyOnWriteArrayList 可以避免多个线程之间的竞争，提高应\n用的性能。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "由于 CopyOnWriteArrayList 读取的数据可能不是最新的，因此它适合于不需要实时更新的数据。例如，在日志应用中，为了保证应用的性能，日志记录的操作可能被缓冲，并不是实时写入文件系统，而是在某个时刻批量写入。这种情况下，使用 CopyOnWriteArrayList 可以避免多个线程之间的竞争，提高应用的性能。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
