      "seed": 79941745,
      "version": 646,
      "versionNonce": 680350872,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "原理",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "c-4F6936h24txjrCGrRpr",
      "originalText": "原理",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "niBvnsLnwzu_-7uLtSSbL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1150.712163065487,
      "y": 3875.105366844181,
      "width": 1441.480609380816,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSd",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1987341087,
      "version": 526,
      "versionNonce": 1896997096,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "很多时候，我们的系统应对的都是读多写少的并发场景。CopyOnWriteArrayList容器允许并发读，读操作是无锁的，性能较高。至于写操作，比如向容器中添加一\n个元素，则首先将当前容器复制一份，然后在新副本上执行写操作，结束之后再将原容器的引用指向新容器。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "很多时候，我们的系统应对的都是读多写少的并发场景。CopyOnWriteArrayList容器允许并发读，读操作是无锁的，性能较高。至于写操作，比如向容器中添加一个元素，则首先将当前容器复制一份，然后在新副本上执行写操作，结束之后再将原容器的引用指向新容器。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LqcnvSCBCfSuX_7RwnIlq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1150.712163065487,
      "y": 3933.9534439181234,
      "width": 493.7599792480469,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSf",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 699570769,
      "version": 452,
      "versionNonce": 1244070296,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 线程安全的，多线程环境下可以直接使用，无需加锁；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 线程安全的，多线程环境下可以直接使用，无需加锁；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "LCYy7XgmPGd0ul4i1brCw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1150.712163065487,
      "y": 3967.801520992066,
      "width": 490.59979248046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSh",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1947709247,
      "version": 454,
      "versionNonce": 284525544,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 通过锁 + 数组拷贝 + volatile 关键字保证了线程安全；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 通过锁 + 数组拷贝 + volatile 关键字保证了线程安全；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Xv3WPYMcheg6jZwq8DhAp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1150.712163065487,
      "y": 4001.6495980660084,
      "width": 837.8025405108964,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSj",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1038952497,
      "version": 526,
      "versionNonce": 1174605464,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 每次数组操作，都会把数组拷贝一份出来，在新数组上进行操作，操作成功之后再赋值回去。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 每次数组操作，都会把数组拷贝一份出来，在新数组上进行操作，操作成功之后再赋值回去。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mDTS0sWw4wFD7DFDSANjy",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -1146.3746212373933,
      "y": 4033.898991045876,
      "width": 633.20093597531,
      "height": 426.5311860389241,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 855754527,
      "version": 620,
      "versionNonce": 1517078248,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "11d327adeecb170758b79f8643d3b328b9eef72e",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "zKjWgigxKuv7XP9iBK2rM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4099.30823053593,
      "width": 784.11962890625,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1225000913,
      "version": 765,
      "versionNonce": 1691712408,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "从整体架构上来说，CopyOnWriteArrayList 数据结构和 ArrayList 是一致的，底层是个数\n组，只不过 CopyOnWriteArrayList 在对数组进行操作的时候，基本会分四步走：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "从整体架构上来说，CopyOnWriteArrayList 数据结构和 ArrayList 是一致的，底层是个数组，只不过 CopyOnWriteArrayList 在对数组进行操作的时候，基本会分四步走：",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "i9p3Y_NRcOVeeMufp4aXC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4160.138021237813,
      "width": 73.75997924804688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1056823743,
      "version": 743,
      "versionNonce": 436447720,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 加锁；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 加锁；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yC44AB5UgEOCgLxATWYUF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4195.967811939693,
      "width": 253.75997924804688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 464840113,
      "version": 695,
      "versionNonce": 953305240,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 从原数组中拷贝出新数组；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 从原数组中拷贝出新数组；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "apiPHhJbG2TtvqY9hEdpa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4231.797602641575,
      "width": 473.7599792480469,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1387940319,
      "version": 702,
      "versionNonce": 717630696,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 在新数组上进行操作，并把新数组赋值给数组容器；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 在新数组上进行操作，并把新数组赋值给数组容器；",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "K7RM1n4qkCPDTiajnuq-9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4267.627393343456,
      "width": 53.759979248046875,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 72288145,
      "version": 694,
      "versionNonce": 1840084376,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 解锁",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 解锁",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B9MCPgCwbBzvJt-ChbGB_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4303.457184045338,
      "width": 788.379638671875,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1907602943,
      "version": 785,
      "versionNonce": 641748968,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "除了加锁之外，CopyOnWriteArrayList 的底层数组还被 volatile 关键字修饰，意思是一旦\n数组被修改，其它线程立马能够感知到，代码如下：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "除了加锁之外，CopyOnWriteArrayList 的底层数组还被 volatile 关键字修饰，意思是一旦数组被修改，其它线程立马能够感知到，代码如下：",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IHMjfum9EnBHCduwW2jrj",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4364.286974747219,
      "width": 428,
      "height": 34,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "ENuQovnC3AhFUQY346EBK",
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YSz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 154044159,
      "version": 664,
      "versionNonce": 412811928,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "status": "saved",
      "fileId": "10ea85e184195384ce94e8bf2c1dd2b0f8013325",
      "scale": [
        1,
        1
      ],
      "crop": null
    },
    {
      "id": "m2-AN_Md-6Fe--WM_msji",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -487.8156366334406,
      "y": 4409.116765449101,
      "width": 785.679443359375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
