      "seed": 1351730641,
      "version": 724,
      "versionNonce": 343806696,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "整体上来说，CopyOnWriteArrayList 就是利用锁 + 数组拷贝 + volatile 关键字保证了 List\n的线程安全。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "整体上来说，CopyOnWriteArrayList 就是利用锁 + 数组拷贝 + volatile 关键字保证了 List 的线程安全。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "j5BCOFJfPn3dF0qPxHw2s",
