      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "缺点",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "RE4bmtrlq2osIen4PxVco",
      "originalText": "缺点",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "C4-ycBk1qLJK-gV09KtwD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -444.04999143518694,
      "y": 4531.894545552638,
      "width": 739.6592354804957,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1980056977,
      "version": 596,
      "versionNonce": 92888808,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 内存占用问题，毕竟每次执行写操作都要将原容器拷贝一份。数据量大时，对内存\n压力较大，可能会引起频繁GC；",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 内存占用问题，毕竟每次执行写操作都要将原容器拷贝一份。数据量大时，对内存压力较大，可能会引起频繁GC；",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YxvIkSLK5HgtaErlAASDi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -444.04999143518694,
      "y": 4585.457852797376,
      "width": 736.8824300006822,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "CO7n1OkvP64npOCvScbsr",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1275615231,
      "version": 602,
      "versionNonce": 2037277592,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 无法保证实时性，因为CopyOnWrite的写时复制机制，所以在进行写操作的时\n候，内存里会同时驻扎两个对象的内存，旧的对象和新写入的对象（注意：在复制\n的时候只是复制容器里的引用，只是在写的时候会创建新对象添加到新容器里，而\n旧容器的对象还在使用，所以有两份对象内存）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 无法保证实时性，因为CopyOnWrite的写时复制机制，所以在进行写操作的时候，内存里会同时驻扎两个对象的内存，旧的对象和新写入的对象（注意：在复制的时候只是复制容器里的引用，只是在写的时候会创建新对象添加到新容器里，而旧容器的对象还在使用，所以有两份对象内存）",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "scNhJ6gL4dJ2eI1vwjVas",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -1165.1832404886866,
      "y": 4749.437340001682,
      "width": 1669.3953207982702,
      "height": 637.6162683604495,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#e9ecef",
      "fillStyle": "cross-hatch",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "lxZ5t5wG7PV5uxnCvlmGS",
        "oxu7jxrJlMwvD3lK793C4",
        "6_Pu1JVdq48biTuPbkjW2",
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTZ",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1436206545,
      "version": 947,
      "versionNonce": 1707950568,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "wrQc3S5zivreh6ZUgFRHG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1145.165600420309,
      "y": 4814.668454156127,
      "width": 1595.1040103770088,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTd",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1226917873,
      "version": 478,
      "versionNonce": 437137560,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在 Java 中，迭代器（Iterator）在迭代的过程中，修改（添加或删除元素）集合，不同的迭代器对此的表现行为是不一样的，可分为两类：Fail-Fast（快速失败）和 Fail-Safe（安全\n失败）。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在 Java 中，迭代器（Iterator）在迭代的过程中，修改（添加或删除元素）集合，不同的迭代器对此的表现行为是不一样的，可分为两类：Fail-Fast（快速失败）和 Fail-Safe（安全失败）。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "R6aLbcEX9J81YSJVVrXGf",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -1146.4537140937643,
      "y": 4876.246818015799,
      "width": 126,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTh",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1970147153,
      "version": 182,
      "versionNonce": 2040317160,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "7zXgoew04g3SU61-XiULs",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "7zXgoew04g3SU61-XiULs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1141.363649091323,
      "y": 4881.246818015799,
      "width": 115.81986999511719,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1248603039,
      "version": 350,
      "versionNonce": 254565784,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "fail-fast 机制",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "R6aLbcEX9J81YSJVVrXGf",
      "originalText": "fail-fast 机制",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Eb3TlxIfyFqEJBgCw11pf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1146.4537140937643,
      "y": 4919.723114324213,
      "width": 795.5197143554688,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 41230801,
      "version": 319,
      "versionNonce": 243525608,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "fail-fast 机制是java集合(Collection)中的一种错误机制。当多个线程对同一个集合的内容进\n行操作时，就可能会产生 fail-fast 事件。例如：当某一个线程A通过 iterator 去遍历某集合\n的过程中，若该集合的内容被其他线程所改变了；那么线程A访问集合时，就会抛出\nConcurrentModificationException异常，产生 fail-fast 事件。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "fail-fast 机制是java集合(Collection)中的一种错误机制。当多个线程对同一个集合的内容进行操作时，就可能会产生 fail-fast 事件。例如：当某一个线程A通过 iterator 去遍历某集合的过程中，若该集合的内容被其他线程所改变了；那么线程A访问集合时，就会抛出ConcurrentModificationException异常，产生 fail-fast 事件。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0CzWOe2p4ujxd8F0gRVQj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1146.4537140937643,
      "y": 5028.199410632627,
      "width": 765.759521484375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YTt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1682137023,
      "version": 293,
      "versionNonce": 2046618264,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在 java.util 包中的集合，如 ArrayList、HashMap 等，它们的迭代器默认都是采用 Fail-\nFast 机制。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在 java.util 包中的集合，如 ArrayList、HashMap 等，它们的迭代器默认都是采用 Fail-Fast 机制。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "loVjaVIGGaCqCVdu9MQvE",
      "type": "image",
      "x": -1146.4537140937643,
      "y": 5086.675706941041,
      "width": 763.1124136802846,
      "height": 96.96403246332403,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "transparent",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
