      "text": "fail-fast解决方案",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "_QAlOQdL86AYfCyH7UxYa",
      "originalText": "fail-fast解决方案",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rCWG57UiwdhhRBnWczaty",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1146.4537140937643,
      "y": 5235.592332021193,
      "width": 798.3397216796875,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YUG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1111799601,
      "version": 349,
      "versionNonce": 621094040,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 方案一：在遍历过程中所有涉及到改变modCount 值的地方全部加上synchronized 或者直\n接使用 Collection#synchronizedList，这样就可以解决问题，但是不推荐，因为增删造成的\n同步锁可能会阻塞遍历操作。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 方案一：在遍历过程中所有涉及到改变modCount 值的地方全部加上synchronized 或者直接使用 Collection#synchronizedList，这样就可以解决问题，但是不推荐，因为增删造成的同步锁可能会阻塞遍历操作。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6W_MQy6h7hH7KZ8goMoxt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1146.4537140937643,
      "y": 5319.068628329607,
      "width": 786.7595825195312,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YUO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2062176351,
      "version": 326,
      "versionNonce": 1958678760,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 方案二：使用CopyOnWriteArrayList 替换 ArrayList，推荐使用该方案（即fail-safe）。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 方案二：使用CopyOnWriteArrayList 替换 ArrayList，推荐使用该方案（即fail-safe）。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pnOBZSLi-L2j6DjtrRdsj",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -311.7560536946296,
