      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "fail-safe机制",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "pnOBZSLi-L2j6DjtrRdsj",
      "originalText": "fail-safe机制",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "W7PYiPhVVxNotSMoHwZRm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -311.7560536946296,
      "y": 4920.707275441372,
      "width": 783.0594482421875,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YUl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1394535551,
      "version": 422,
      "versionNonce": 1120329368,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "任何对集合结构的修改都会在一个复制的集合上进行，因此不会抛出\nConcurrentModificationException。在 java.util.concurrent 包中的集合，如\nCopyOnWriteArrayList、ConcurrentHashMap 等，它们的迭代器一般都是采用 Fail-Safe\n机制。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "任何对集合结构的修改都会在一个复制的集合上进行，因此不会抛出ConcurrentModificationException。在 java.util.concurrent 包中的集合，如 CopyOnWriteArrayList、ConcurrentHashMap 等，它们的迭代器一般都是采用 Fail-Safe 机制。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "SHrQQtK2UScdusaY1G53P",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -311.7560536946296,
      "y": 5029.183571749786,
      "width": 70,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YUt",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 472570015,
      "version": 301,
      "versionNonce": 1485698792,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "LgOlLWKm2zvrxYDPJRTLf",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "LgOlLWKm2zvrxYDPJRTLf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -306.7560536946296,
      "y": 5034.183571749786,
      "width": 60,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 603152113,
      "version": 416,
      "versionNonce": 949963672,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "缺点：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "SHrQQtK2UScdusaY1G53P",
      "originalText": "缺点：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "jwnLCNq4Tmy_W0kEfB0VN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -311.7560536946296,
      "y": 5072.6598680582,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YVG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1319830687,
      "version": 369,
      "versionNonce": 478075368,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 采用 Fail-Safe 机制的集合类都是线程安全的，但是它们无法保证数据的实时一致性，它\n们只能保证数据的最终一致性。在迭代过程中，如果集合被修改了，可能读取到的仍然是旧\n的数据。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 采用 Fail-Safe 机制的集合类都是线程安全的，但是它们无法保证数据的实时一致性，它们只能保证数据的最终一致性。在迭代过程中，如果集合被修改了，可能读取到的仍然是旧的数据。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "D0P2ABgMZWqZOidgwG_x3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -311.7560536946296,
      "y": 5156.136164366614,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "KvEh5edbYabu0Q0VY8dAC",
        "2j6AWX3xj9qij90x5ynAu"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9YVV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 149706961,
      "version": 386,
      "versionNonce": 316807320,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059001225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Fail-Safe 机制还存在另外一个问题，就是内存占用。由于这类集合一般都是通过复制来实\n现读写分离的，因此它们会创建出更多的对象，导致占用更多的内存，甚至可能引起频繁的\n垃圾回收，严重影响性能。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Fail-Safe 机制还存在另外一个问题，就是内存占用。由于这类集合一般都是通过复制来实现读写分离的，因此它们会创建出更多的对象，导致占用更多的内存，甚至可能引起频繁的垃圾回收，严重影响性能。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
