      "text": "JDK1.7 中的ConcurrentHashMap",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "x-xA52oqRYnyfvErVG7rs",
      "originalText": "JDK1.7 中的ConcurrentHashMap",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CHsD4vCz5x0lgH4yvB39-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1635.4421746331432,
      "y": 8464.912286387775,
      "width": 750.8705964358564,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "amitogeAu5Nbwrtc95m6i",
        "63rKdsA1XaPZshOcGORoe",
        "SgVpKiRrzwRVufgT1Gz-F",
        "d4nLWB_aWwuTNaqgPhz7X",
        "ajuUIlaJES67Crmgb_VYd"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9aO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1340216040,
      "version": 313,
      "versionNonce": 780276376,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767943926404,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "在jdk1.7中，结构是用Segments数组 + HashEntry数组 + 链表实现的 （写分散的思\n想）。ConcurrentHashMap内部维护了一个Segment数组。每个Segment继承自\nReentrantLock并且它内部本质上是一个Hash表。这样做的好处是能够减小锁的粒\n度，提高并发访问的效率。默认Segment 数量为 16，可以通过构造函数来修改默认\n值。当需要put或get一个元素时，线程首先通过hash定位到具体的Segment，然后在\n对应的Segment上进行锁定操作。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "在jdk1.7中，结构是用Segments数组 + HashEntry数组 + 链表实现的 （写分散的思想）。ConcurrentHashMap内部维护了一个Segment数组。每个Segment继承自ReentrantLock并且它内部本质上是一个Hash表。这样做的好处是能够减小锁的粒度，提高并发访问的效率。默认Segment 数量为 16，可以通过构造函数来修改默认值。当需要put或get一个元素时，线程首先通过hash定位到具体的Segment，然后在对应的Segment上进行锁定操作。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
