      "updated": 1767944057738,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "应用场景",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "OyV0d-NF1p_Z1BSsrqwTp",
      "originalText": "应用场景",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oHLLbafJggZ6_b9NEQGmk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 859.6618228671136,
      "y": 3259.645904928611,
      "width": 511.5998229980469,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "L7k_3y9Y35DRjHxQ8Y2qH",
        "yI4P1mxbo5oYIQXScdWeK"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9ah",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 558959441,
      "version": 271,
      "versionNonce": 189975448,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767944057738,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ConcurrentHashMap 的应用场景包括但不限于以下几种：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ConcurrentHashMap 的应用场景包括但不限于以下几种：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "NGZJWrRoSU0Z-54fQ29rI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 859.6618228671136,
      "y": 3292.450814316255,
      "width": 736.6599731445312,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "L7k_3y9Y35DRjHxQ8Y2qH",
        "yI4P1mxbo5oYIQXScdWeK"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9ai",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 546623039,
      "version": 291,
      "versionNonce": 1126537368,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767944057738,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.共享数据的线程安全：在多线程编程中，如果需要进行共享数据的读写，可以使用\nConcurrentHashMap 保证线程安全。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.共享数据的线程安全：在多线程编程中，如果需要进行共享数据的读写，可以使用 ConcurrentHashMap 保证线程安全。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7kIKVJszz-q6Mh8_CgDS-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 859.6618228671136,
      "y": 3351.5438373773536,
      "width": 796.8197631835938,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "L7k_3y9Y35DRjHxQ8Y2qH",
        "yI4P1mxbo5oYIQXScdWeK"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9aj",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2056616241,
      "version": 274,
      "versionNonce": 1897317784,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767944057738,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.缓存：ConcurrentHashMap 的高并发性能和线程安全能力，使其成为一种很好的缓存实\n现方案。在多线程环境下，使用 ConcurrentHashMap 作为缓存的数据结构，能够提高程序\n的并发性能，同时保证数据的一致性。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.缓存：ConcurrentHashMap 的高并发性能和线程安全能力，使其成为一种很好的缓存实现方案。在多线程环境下，使用 ConcurrentHashMap 作为缓存的数据结构，能够提高程序的并发性能，同时保证数据的一致性。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
