    {
      "id": "Ni-AHJTSpj9X7HamZqfD0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -441.1968535540889,
      "y": 2833.9224019076883,
      "width": 455.45454545454544,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "7wL6XproqRpKszAVe5b7m",
        "EohJx-zrZgOIz_vlE3CZD"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9cN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1831253553,
      "version": 1135,
      "versionNonce": 1251323544,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059286477,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "原理：利用高并发往往是读多写少的特性，对读操\n作不加锁，对写操作，先复制一份新的集合，在新\n的集合上面修改，然后将新集合赋值给旧的引用，\n并通过volatile 保证其可见性，当然写操作的锁是必\n不可少的了。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "原理：利用高并发往往是读多写少的特性，对读操作不加锁，对写操作，先复制一份新的集合，在新的集合上面修改，然后将新集合赋值给旧的引用，并通过volatile 保证其可见性，当然写操作的锁是必不可少的了。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "J1mv2pj5as8E67qPnVEL-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 38.33333693309646,
      "y": 2829.7906722163707,
      "width": 519.0313056689404,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "7wL6XproqRpKszAVe5b7m",
        "EohJx-zrZgOIz_vlE3CZD"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9cO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 262249969,
      "version": 925,
      "versionNonce": 2115247000,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059286477,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "原理：基于CopyOnWriteArrayList实现，其唯一的不同是\n在add时调用的是CopyOnWriteArrayList的addIfAbsent方\n法，其遍历当前Object数组，如Object数组中已有了当前元\n素，则直接返回，如果没有则放入Object数组的尾部，并\n返回。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "原理：基于CopyOnWriteArrayList实现，其唯一的不同是在add时调用的是CopyOnWriteArrayList的addIfAbsent方法，其遍历当前Object数组，如Object数组中已有了当前元素，则直接返回，如果没有则放入Object数组的尾部，并返回。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YSFyLccLFchBhaZrAv7S5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 613.7391038699711,
      "y": 2844.14544669458,
      "width": 242.06348882738274,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "7wL6XproqRpKszAVe5b7m",
        "EohJx-zrZgOIz_vlE3CZD"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9cP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1389729201,
      "version": 957,
      "versionNonce": 1899817112,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059286477,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "原理：JDK6中采用一种更\n加细粒度的加锁机制\nSegment“分段锁”，JDK8\n中采用CAS无锁算法。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "原理：JDK6中采用一种更加细粒度的加锁机制Segment“分段锁”，JDK8中采用CAS无锁算法。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hXqmhwzdQjP437eyOdSes",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 890.6604645504997,
      "y": 2844.3159423427055,
      "width": 233.0197817398701,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "7wL6XproqRpKszAVe5b7m",
        "EohJx-zrZgOIz_vlE3CZD"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9cQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 129932657,
      "version": 860,
      "versionNonce": 2143557016,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059286477,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "原理：Skip list（跳表）是\n一种可以代替平衡树的数\n据结构，默认是按照Key\n值升序的。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "原理：Skip list（跳表）是一种可以代替平衡树的数据结构，默认是按照Key值升序的。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
