      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "案例三：在活动中，创建一个用户列表，记录冻结的用户。一旦冻结，不允许再下单抢购，但是可以浏览。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "EtHwmP36XZuZxljaKADZo",
      "originalText": "案例三：在活动中，创建一个用户列表，记录冻结的用户。一旦冻结，不允许再下单抢购，但是可以浏览。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DqGn8SWLGQPTiYvQjGtYB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 6339.416666666661,
      "width": 1041,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "iyxjLOPooTawLwjpSx-uk",
        "ARU2QBdKjcq-eiVt2y3dx",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1692649951,
      "version": 481,
      "versionNonce": 307878376,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "场景分析：违规被冻结的用户不会太多，但是绝大多数非冻结用户每次抢单都要去查一下这个列表。低频写，高频读。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "场景分析：违规被冻结的用户不会太多，但是绝大多数非冻结用户每次抢单都要去查一下这个列表。低频写，高频读。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "I3oE4CdGfG_-EDliRDOQ1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 6373.166666666661,
      "width": 358.9598693847656,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "iyxjLOPooTawLwjpSx-uk",
        "ARU2QBdKjcq-eiVt2y3dx",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 595429265,
      "version": 492,
      "versionNonce": 1010243736,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "初级方案：ArrayList记录要冻结的用户id",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "初级方案：ArrayList记录要冻结的用户id",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ibR1jZcy7PRB2fgFcsSkN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 6406.916666666661,
      "width": 1019.1997680664062,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "iyxjLOPooTawLwjpSx-uk",
        "ARU2QBdKjcq-eiVt2y3dx",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dL",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 44905983,
      "version": 496,
      "versionNonce": 416701672,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "问题：ArrayList对冻结用户id的插入和读取操作在高并发时，线程不安全。Vector可以做到线程安全，但并发性能\n差，锁太重。可以使用CopyOnWriteArrayList。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "问题：ArrayList对冻结用户id的插入和读取操作在高并发时，线程不安全。Vector可以做到线程安全，但并发性能差，锁太重。可以使用CopyOnWriteArrayList。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YWodRETktE2zsMi6kgDx1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 6465.666666666661,
      "width": 1014.9797973632812,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "iyxjLOPooTawLwjpSx-uk",
        "ARU2QBdKjcq-eiVt2y3dx",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dM",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 845704561,
      "version": 566,
      "versionNonce": 1274561944,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "选型：综合业务场景，选CopyOnWriteArrayList，会占空间，但是也仅仅发生在添加新冻结用户的时候。绝大多数\n的访问在非冻结用户的读取和比对上，不会阻塞。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "选型：综合业务场景，选CopyOnWriteArrayList，会占空间，但是也仅仅发生在添加新冻结用户的时候。绝大多数的访问在非冻结用户的读取和比对上，不会阻塞。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
