      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "案例二：在一次活动下，为每个用户记录浏览商品的历史和次数。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "iSD4pLfQcyQkS6Rb9QKIO",
      "originalText": "案例二：在一次活动下，为每个用户记录浏览商品的历史和次数。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7c7wPwwTTT9_PcKEWVEqM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -429.59749508914865,
      "y": 6023.36666666666,
      "width": 780,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "AFb-fPB7odP3KXfk-0fwq",
        "LLZcObe2RwOpM_JupQK1c",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1185115519,
      "version": 350,
      "versionNonce": 1311096728,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "场景分析：每个用户各自浏览的商品量级非常大，并且每次访问都要更新次数，频繁读写",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "场景分析：每个用户各自浏览的商品量级非常大，并且每次访问都要更新次数，频繁读写",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VRyiUJzxLq0FdIvR-kJED",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -429.59749508914865,
      "y": 6055.56666666666,
      "width": 606.3798217773438,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "AFb-fPB7odP3KXfk-0fwq",
        "LLZcObe2RwOpM_JupQK1c",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dR",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2041802225,
      "version": 401,
      "versionNonce": 1607050728,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "初级方案：为确保线程安全，采用上面的思路，ConcurrentHashMap",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "初级方案：为确保线程安全，采用上面的思路，ConcurrentHashMap",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TMzXVzqzGk57UW5Gx77V7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -429.59749508914865,
      "y": 6087.76666666666,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "AFb-fPB7odP3KXfk-0fwq",
        "LLZcObe2RwOpM_JupQK1c",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1073178015,
      "version": 427,
      "versionNonce": 393874584,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "问题：ConcurrentHashMap 内部机制在数据量大时，会把链表转换为红黑树。而红黑树在\n高并发情况下，删除和插入过程中有个平衡的过程，会牵涉到大量节点，因此竞争锁资源的\n代价相对比较高",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "问题：ConcurrentHashMap 内部机制在数据量大时，会把链表转换为红黑树。而红黑树在高并发情况下，删除和插入过程中有个平衡的过程，会牵涉到大量节点，因此竞争锁资源的代价相对比较高",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t71lQWuez2HdgI355n5nq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -429.59749508914865,
      "y": 6169.96666666666,
      "width": 898.5597534179688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "AFb-fPB7odP3KXfk-0fwq",
        "LLZcObe2RwOpM_JupQK1c",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dT",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1775405009,
      "version": 533,
      "versionNonce": 1047308520,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "选型：用跳表，ConcurrentSkipListMap将key值分层，逐个切段，增删效率高于ConcurrentHashMap",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "选型：用跳表，ConcurrentSkipListMap将key值分层，逐个切段，增删效率高于ConcurrentHashMap",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZAUaZ6xzYsNq1mogb1lC4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -429.59749508914865,
      "y": 6202.16666666666,
      "width": 884.1998901367189,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "AFb-fPB7odP3KXfk-0fwq",
        "LLZcObe2RwOpM_JupQK1c",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dU",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 945248703,
      "version": 431,
      "versionNonce": 717011352,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "结论：如果对数据有强一致要求，则需使用Hashtable；在大部分场景通常都是弱一致性的情况下，\n使用ConcurrentHashMap 即可；如果数据量级很高，且存在大量增删改操作，则可以考虑使用\nConcurrentSkipListMap。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "结论：如果对数据有强一致要求，则需使用Hashtable；在大部分场景通常都是弱一致性的情况下，使用ConcurrentHashMap 即可；如果数据量级很高，且存在大量增删改操作，则可以考虑使用ConcurrentSkipListMap。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
