      "seed": 247098655,
      "version": 510,
      "versionNonce": 364220136,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "案例一：电商网站中记录一次活动下各个商品售卖的数量。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "uLrgtvrj4mGyREP-5HSS0",
      "originalText": "案例一：电商网站中记录一次活动下各个商品售卖的数量。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mvkXi0ECtyN_4CX5ZXjbJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 5800.916666666661,
      "width": 821.8598632812499,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Lq5Q6BdIMJF7l79GvFZxx",
        "kzuLr-yFIzVZ8IV0pT07m",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 574994513,
      "version": 452,
      "versionNonce": 1969042328,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "场景分析：需要频繁按商品id做get和set，但是商品id（key）的数量相对稳定不会频繁增删",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "场景分析：需要频繁按商品id做get和set，但是商品id（key）的数量相对稳定不会频繁增删",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3G2b7P4FqEqUjsurZL8cL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 5832.666666666661,
      "width": 945.6998291015625,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Lq5Q6BdIMJF7l79GvFZxx",
        "kzuLr-yFIzVZ8IV0pT07m",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9dZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1481470271,
      "version": 514,
      "versionNonce": 15954408,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "初级方案：选用HashMap，key为商品id，value为商品购买的次数。每次下单取出次数，增加后再写入",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "初级方案：选用HashMap，key为商品id，value为商品购买的次数。每次下单取出次数，增加后再写入",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "O4ir162mRCxbb-z1VNfVJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 5864.416666666661,
      "width": 909.8199462890624,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Lq5Q6BdIMJF7l79GvFZxx",
        "kzuLr-yFIzVZ8IV0pT07m",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9da",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 845973041,
      "version": 546,
      "versionNonce": 1336082584,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "问题：HashMap线程不安全！在多次商品id写入后，如果发生扩容，在JDK1.7 之前，在并发场景下\nHashMap 会出现死循环，从而导致CPU 使用率居高不下。JDK1.8 中修复了HashMap 扩容导致的死循\n环问题，但在高并发场景下，依然会有数据丢失以及不准确的情况出现。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "问题：HashMap线程不安全！在多次商品id写入后，如果发生扩容，在JDK1.7 之前，在并发场景下HashMap 会出现死循环，从而导致CPU 使用率居高不下。JDK1.8 中修复了HashMap 扩容导致的死循环问题，但在高并发场景下，依然会有数据丢失以及不准确的情况出现。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bzSqBUkCEb8ksKLJctgWM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -432.33333333333303,
      "y": 5946.166666666661,
      "width": 790.0197143554688,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "Lq5Q6BdIMJF7l79GvFZxx",
        "kzuLr-yFIzVZ8IV0pT07m",
        "C2Da5kEGs3xYD7oWU8dyj",
        "Cv9qRQ_p8csusHxlWCaT7",
        "Gabkos1d6P6f0roRVU4u0"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9db",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1563095391,
      "version": 488,
      "versionNonce": 813495528,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767945318615,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "选型：Hashtable 不推荐，锁太重，选ConcurrentHashMap 确保高并发下多线程的安全性",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "选型：Hashtable 不推荐，锁太重，选ConcurrentHashMap 确保高并发下多线程的安全性",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
