      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 一个跳表结构由很多层数据结构组成。",
      "fontSize": 19.585710929494294,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 一个跳表结构由很多层数据结构组成。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "v4OFqHukuUeyD5BPUQNyT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2275.885959421723,
      "y": 4836.044356975831,
      "width": 601.0463065676563,
      "height": 24.482138661867868,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fiz0jmVQ5Il9e4qAYeLSK",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eN",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1743339665,
      "version": 404,
      "versionNonce": 1166335208,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 每一层都是一个有序的链表，默认是升序。也可以自定义排序方法。",
      "fontSize": 19.585710929494294,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 每一层都是一个有序的链表，默认是升序。也可以自定义排序方法。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QIwsJ36HnP3QV4Nt7bTOk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2275.885959421723,
      "y": 4870.070154251946,
      "width": 464.2400440001231,
      "height": 24.482138661867868,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fiz0jmVQ5Il9e4qAYeLSK",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1454738687,
      "version": 404,
      "versionNonce": 1735509400,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 最底层链表（图中所示Level1）包含了所有的元素。",
      "fontSize": 19.585710929494297,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 最底层链表（图中所示Level1）包含了所有的元素。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "avWoznDqjTCJzR5DbEQtI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2275.885959421723,
      "y": 4904.095951528062,
      "width": 746.4309407731045,
      "height": 24.482138661867868,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fiz0jmVQ5Il9e4qAYeLSK",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1123354225,
      "version": 404,
      "versionNonce": 1437138920,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 如果每一个元素出现在LevelN的链表中（N>1)，那么这个元素必定在下层链表出现。",
      "fontSize": 19.585710929494294,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 如果每一个元素出现在LevelN的链表中（N>1)，那么这个元素必定在下层链表出现。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "k9mi7d3pvulzJER8GXLYm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2275.885959421723,
      "y": 4938.121748804176,
      "width": 999.5363564515441,
      "height": 24.482138661867868,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "fiz0jmVQ5Il9e4qAYeLSK",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1469682975,
      "version": 526,
      "versionNonce": 1968525976,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- 每一个节点都包含了两个指针，一个指向同一级链表中的下一个元素，一个指向下一层级别链表中的相同值元素。",
      "fontSize": 19.585710929494297,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- 每一个节点都包含了两个指针，一个指向同一级链表中的下一个元素，一个指向下一层级别链表中的相同值元素。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
