      "text": "跳表的插入",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "EcEOrmhpiPr8XNd0GXaNU",
      "originalText": "跳表的插入",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vUo_DiUw2dpxyf5URpblh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 887.7772453784117,
      "y": 5588.166666666663,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "alWNIxZDmbMQYRwn6spyU",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 402151153,
      "version": 320,
      "versionNonce": 1733676008,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "跳表插入数据的流程如下：",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "跳表插入数据的流程如下：",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "murGuvl_yNg9OvaJpOMvD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 887.7772453784117,
      "y": 5623.166666666663,
      "width": 1130.714858015015,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "alWNIxZDmbMQYRwn6spyU",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1133612191,
      "version": 394,
      "versionNonce": 984303256,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.找到元素适合的插入层级K，这里的K采用随机的方式。若K大于跳表的总层级，那么开辟新的一层，否则在对应的层级插入。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.找到元素适合的插入层级K，这里的K采用随机的方式。若K大于跳表的总层级，那么开辟新的一层，否则在对应的层级插入。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KCh8BAdw0sCOAzB0QLVyW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 887.7772453784117,
      "y": 5658.0746444024035,
      "width": 156.6599884033203,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "alWNIxZDmbMQYRwn6spyU",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9eZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 563237073,
      "version": 340,
      "versionNonce": 226758376,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2.申请新的节点。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2.申请新的节点。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "t967t9fWmGHQAMWlKBRXo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 887.7772453784117,
      "y": 5693.0746444024035,
      "width": 176.6599884033203,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "alWNIxZDmbMQYRwn6spyU",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9ea",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 873767103,
      "version": 340,
      "versionNonce": 129414040,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3.调整对应的指针。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3.调整对应的指针。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
