      "version": 395,
      "versionNonce": 1960060824,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ConcurrentSkipListMap 是 Java 中的一种线程安全、基于跳表实现的有序映射（Map）数据结构。它是对 TreeMap 的并发实现，支持高并发读写操作。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ConcurrentSkipListMap 是 Java 中的一种线程安全、基于跳表实现的有序映射（Map）数据结构。它是对 TreeMap 的并发实现，支持高并发读写操作。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1BWbuhBoTx8SK5_1OkooM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 843.2324150933157,
      "y": 4777.074761742592,
      "width": 1092.9819878472224,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "23Ceb6XRdmWfEKzhNTntX",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9ej",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 683226897,
      "version": 426,
      "versionNonce": 261471720,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ConcurrentSkipListMap适用于需要高并发性能、支持有序性和区间查询的场景，能够有效地提高系统的性能和可扩展性。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ConcurrentSkipListMap适用于需要高并发性能、支持有序性和区间查询的场景，能够有效地提高系统的性能和可扩展性。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rt1ifaxwsuJBnL2pFnZ0i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 843.2324150933157,
      "y": 4812.038412374076,
      "width": 1123.3333333333333,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "23Ceb6XRdmWfEKzhNTntX",
        "9A16PABKWTQze51rScygH",
        "mVDNs0mVHfa3kLaj2aooM",
        "Ho9qNMp180B66R_s-vjW7"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9ek",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 847374879,
      "version": 403,
      "versionNonce": 739996824,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768059061416,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "跳表是一种基于有序链表的数据结构，支持快速插入、删除、查找操作，其时间复杂度为O(log n)，比普通链表的O(n)更高效。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "跳表是一种基于有序链表的数据结构，支持快速插入、删除、查找操作，其时间复杂度为O(log n)，比普通链表的O(n)更高效。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
